        "<<ref _top 'subjCap'>> <<verb _top 'slide'>> <<pro _top 'poss'>> <<=_top.body.Finger.toLowerCase()>> back and forth, caressing the walls of <<ref _bottom 'poss'>> insides. <<pro _bottom 'subj' true>> <<verbEx _bottom 'contunue'>> to tense.",
